  "subject": "Prototype of actor service interface",
  "commit_message": "Prototype of actor service interface\n\nThis is by no means final. Just a start to prototype how an\nenforcement PDP engine can use the actor service provider for\nsimplifying asynchronous calling of operations during runtime.\n\nAdding the usage of a callback interface so enforcement PDP\nengines can customize how they handle operations being finished.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-1625\nChange-Id: I3d1e35f44ebb2deedb06699ac54d97684b8887bd\nSigned-off-by: Pamela Dragosh <pdragosh@research.att.com>\n",
